We have some updates on the way, but if you have any more issues, or would like us to take a look at your account email us at ios-support@myswimpro.com

Happy Swimming!", 'modified': '2019-03-29T20:03:39Z'}

{'id': 16153359, 'body': "Hi there, thank you for taking the time to leave us a review. We greatly appreciate the feedback.

